      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V alloy modeled as linear elastic isotropic (E = 114 GPa, nu = 0.34) below yield threshold, consistent with published material characterization. Frictional contact (mu = 0.2) applied at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces, consistent with literature values for titanium-on-titanium contact. Geometric nonlinearity (large displacement) enabled to capture post-yield behavior for the 40 mm displacement QoI. Model form judged appropriate for the COU."
